dct_title_s: Automobile road from Los Angeles to San Francisco via coast route
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, drainage.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and San Francisco.
Numbered 140 in lower right corner and 93 in lower right margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
